1. PURPOSE OF THIS LICENSE
================================================================================

This repository ("the Software") — including all source code, configuration,
build scripts, infrastructure manifests, schemas, tests, assets, and
documentation — is published publicly for one purpose and one purpose only:

    Personal, non-commercial reading and study of the source code.

The Software is NOT open source. It is NOT free software. It is published
under a deliberately restrictive license so that the public can read and
learn from it without any of the rights normally granted by an open-source
license.

